dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Washington County, WI 2017
dc_description_s: These line and polygon data layers represent roads and right of ways for Washington County, Wisconsin in 2017. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Washington_Transportation_2017.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'Right_of_Way' and 'Washington_Roads_2017'.
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
